description:
It was a wonderful experience covering Genshin Impact's music. It was one of my passion projects. I hope you enjoy the journey through Teyvat with me!

Check out Genshin Impact here: https://hoyo.link/7yqkF0AL. And here is a special redemption code: LA5E77CLZX5V (includes 60 Primogems & 5 Adventurer's Experience, valid from September 27, 00:00 to December 11, 23:59 Beijing Time).

Director: Takumi Osera (THINGS.)
Assistant Director: Takumi Saitoh (THINGS.)
Stylist: Yuki Tsuchida
Editor: Dennis
